where: Wwet is the wet mass of BCH in g, Wdry is the dry mass of BCH in g.

The porosity of BCH membranes was determined by the liquid displacement method [52].The dimensions of samples were measured, and their volumes were calculated. The samples were weighed and soaked in water at room temperature. After immersion for 24 h, the samples were wiped by a filter paper and weighed. The porosity of three samples was calculated as Eq. (3):3P%=(mf-mi)/ρVMTP×100\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
